Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
fill_setting_save(25.10)                              fill_setting_save(25.10)

Name
       fill_setting_save

Syntax
        fill_setting_save {0 | 1}

       Type: Integer

       Default: 0

       Specifies whether metal fill settings are to be saved in the .init file
       when  saving the design. By default, these metal fill settings are lost
       when you exit Innovus. To enable Innovus to record metal fill  settings
       in  the .init file, you must set the fill_setting_save to 1 before sav-
       ing the design. You can easily reload your settings  by  restoring  the
       saved design:

       set fill_setting_save 1

       saveDesign

       restoreDesign

       #The previous metal fill settings are reloaded.

Related Information
              * saveDesign

              * restoreDesign

